Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.97,0:20:16.10,Default CN,,0,0,0,,美墨...？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:22.20,Default JP,,0,0,0,,どうしたの...？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:22.20,Default CN,,0,0,0,,怎么了...？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.37,0:20:24.10,Default JP,,0,0,0,,こんな所で？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.37,0:20:24.10,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你怎么到这来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:25.42,Default JP,,0,0,0,,あ...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:25.42,Default CN,,0,0,0,,呃...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:26.95,Default JP,,0,0,0,,あの...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:26.95,Default CN,,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:30.62,Default JP,,0,0,0,,来た！来た！歩いてるよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:30.62,Default CN,,0,0,0,,来了！来了！走过来了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.30,0:20:32.60,Default JP,,0,0,0,,そりゃ  歩くメポ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.30,0:20:32.60,Default CN,,0,0,0,,那不废话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:34.90,Default JP,,0,0,0,,えと...あの...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:34.90,Default CN,,0,0,0,,呃...那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:38.35,Default JP,,0,0,0,,勇気...ちょこっと勇気...！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:38.35,Default CN,,0,0,0,,勇气...鼓起一点勇气来吧...！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.02,0:20:40.87,Default JP,,0,0,0,,えと...あの...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.02,0:20:40.87,Default CN,,0,0,0,,呃...那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:43.06,Default JP,,0,0,0,,勇気なんです！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:43.06,Default CN,,0,0,0,,要有勇气！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.60,0:20:44.30,Default JP,,0,0,0,,...えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.60,0:20:44.30,Default CN,,0,0,0,,...欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.50,0:20:45.42,Default JP,,0,0,0,,あっ！いえっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.50,0:20:45.42,Default CN,,0,0,0,,呃！不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.42,0:20:46.92,Default JP,,0,0,0,,そうじゃなくて...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.42,0:20:46.92,Default CN,,0,0,0,,讲错了...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:49.12,Default JP,,0,0,0,,なぎさ  頑張って！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:49.12,Default CN,,0,0,0,,渚 加油呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.70,0:20:50.88,Default JP,,0,0,0,,なぎささん！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.70,0:20:50.88,Default CN,,0,0,0,,渚！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.70,0:20:53.10,Default JP,,0,0,0,,これです！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.70,0:20:53.10,Default CN,,0,0,0,,这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.80,0:20:55.32,Default JP,,0,0,0,,せっ...先輩！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.80,0:20:55.32,Default CN,,0,0,0,,学...学长！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:57.90,Default JP,,0,0,0,,お誕生日  おめでとうございます！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:57.90,Default CN,,0,0,0,,生日快乐！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:21:01.06,Default JP,,0,0,0,,これ...よかったら...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:21:01.06,Default CN,,0,0,0,,这个...如果你不嫌弃...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.00,0:21:05.17,Default JP,,0,0,0,,誕生日  覚えてくれてたんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.00,0:21:05.17,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你记得我的生日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:06.72,Default JP,,0,0,0,,はっ...はい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:06.72,Default CN,,0,0,0,,是...是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.50,0:21:10.35,Default JP,,0,0,0,,こういうの欲しかったんだ  どうも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.50,0:21:10.35,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我正想要这种毛巾呢 你真是有心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.72,0:21:11.50,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.72,0:21:11.50,Default CN,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.92,0:21:12.40,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.92,0:21:12.40,Default CN,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.15,0:21:14.67,Default JP,,0,0,0,,イニシャル入れてくれたんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.15,0:21:14.67,Default CN,,0,0,0,,还绣了名字的首字母啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.80,0:21:16.02,Default JP,,0,0,0,,はっ...はい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.80,0:21:16.02,Default CN,,0,0,0,,呃...是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.70,0:21:19.07,Default JP,,0,0,0,,よかったら...部活で  使ってください
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.70,0:21:19.07,Default CN,,0,0,0,,如果你愿意...就在社团活动时用它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.22,0:21:20.39,Default JP,,0,0,0,,毎日使わせてもらうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.22,0:21:20.39,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我会每天都用的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.22,0:21:22.42,Default JP,,0,0,0,,本当ですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.22,0:21:22.42,Default CN,,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.65,0:21:29.35,Default JP,,0,0,0,,美墨さん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.65,0:21:29.35,Default CN,,0,0,0,,美墨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.82,0:21:32.70,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.82,0:21:32.70,Default CN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:49.92,Default JP,,0,0,0,,やった！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:49.92,Default CN,,0,0,0,,成了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.05,0:21:51.80,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ついに渡せた！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.05,0:21:51.80,Default CN,,0,0,0,,终于送出去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.12,0:21:52.72,Default JP,,0,0,0,,やった！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.12,0:21:52.72,Default CN,,0,0,0,,太好啦！
